 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>大規模槍擊案。兇手{{Link-en|尼達爾·馬利克·哈桑|Nidal Malik Hasan}}是一名美國陸軍[[少校|少校]]及[[精神科醫師|精神科]][[軍醫|醫官]]，在該案中槍殺了13人並造成30多人受傷。<ref name=CNN20130806>{{cite web|last=Rubin|first=Josh|title='I am the shooter,' Nidal Hasan tells Fort Hood court-martial|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/08/06/justice/hasan-court-martial/index.html?hpt=hp_t2|work=CNN|publisher=CNN|accessdate=7 August 2013|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928010913/http://www.cnn.com/2013/08/06/justice/hasan-court-martial/index.html?hpt=hp_t2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Stripes 1" />這是在美國軍事基地所曾發生過最嚴重的槍擊案。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/military/2011-03-10-fort-hood-shooting_N.htm| work=USA Today| title=Most Popular E-mail Newsletter| date=March 11, 2011| accessdate=2013-10-01| archive-date=2011-12-01| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111201170136/http://www.usatoday.com/news/military/2011-03-10-fort-hood-shooting_N.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FPM">[http://frontpagemag.com/2013/deborah-weiss/fort-hood-trial-dont-say-the-t-word/ ''-{FortHood Trial: Don’t Say the “T” Word}-''] {{Wayback|url=http://frontpagemag.com/2013/deborah-weiss/fort-hood-trial-dont-say-the-t-word/ |date=20190822025932 }}, ''[[FrontPage_Magazine|FrontPage Magazine]]'', 22 August 2013, retrieved 22 August 2013</ref>參議員[[喬·李伯曼|喬·李伯曼]]<ref name=Google2 />、{{Link-en|巴利·麥卡夫瑞|Barry McCaffrey}}<ref name="Anderson Cooper 360" />將軍等多人都稱此事件為[[恐怖袭击|恐怖攻擊]]。<ref name=MainJ /><ref name=RASM1 />[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]和聯邦執法機構已將此槍擊案歸類為一起{{Link-en|職場暴力|workplace violence}}事件。<ref name="AZAP_2013">{{Citation
