=== 事前準備 ===

根據審判前的證詞，2009年7月31日，哈桑進入[[基林_(得克萨斯州)|基林市]]的一家槍枝店購買他在槍擊案中所使用的[[FN_Five-seveN手槍|FN Five-seveN]][[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]。<ref name="purchase01">{{cite web|url=http://blog.mysanantonio.com/military/2010/10/hasan-sought-gun-with-high-magazine-capacity/|script-title=en:Hasan sought gun with ‘high magazine capacity’ | a mySA.com blog|publisher=Blog.mysanantonio.com|date=October 21, 2010|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archive-date=2012-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609121219/http://blog.mysanantonio.com/military/2010/10/hasan-sought-gun-with-high-magazine-capacity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>據一位該槍枝店的常客，{{Link-en|陸軍專業軍士|Specialist (rank)}}威廉·吉伯特（William Gilbert）所述，哈桑進入店後便要求要「市面上技術最先進的武器，且擁有最高規格的彈匣容量」。<ref name="purchase01"/>據說他被問及要如何使用該武器時，只僅僅反覆說要一把有最大[[彈匣|彈匣]]容量的最先進手槍。<ref name="purchase01"/>當時與哈桑同時在場的三人——吉伯特、店經理以及一名職員，都推薦FN Five-seven手槍。<ref name="purchase02">{{cite web|url=http://kdhnews.com/news/prosecutors-end-case-in-hasan-article-hearing/article_c2cea5e3-063c-5bb4-a978-3cb69bae0501.html|title=Prosecutors end case in Hasan Article 32 hearing|publisher=KDH News|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122150403/https://kdhnews.com/news/prosecutors-end-case-in-hasan-article-hearing/article_c2cea5e3-063c-5bb4-a978-3cb69bae0501.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>吉伯特因為自己擁有一把這樣的槍枝，便花了一小時向哈桑描述如何操作。<ref name="purchase03">{{cite web|url=http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/732007|title=Access|publisher=Medscape|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210161027/https://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/732007|dead-url=no}}</ref>就在要離開該店時，哈桑說要研究研究這個武器。<ref name="purchase03"/>隔天他便回到店中來買這把槍。往後哈桑每週一次來店中買額外彈匣，連同數百發[[5.7×28mm|5.7×28mm]] SS192和SS197SR彈藥。<ref name="purchase02"/>就在槍擊案發前數週，哈桑還造訪了一家在{{Link-en|佛羅倫斯 (德克薩斯州)|Florence, Texas|佛羅倫斯}}的戶外射擊場。據稱也就是在那兒，他變得善於在100碼的距離外擊中人形標靶。<ref name="purchase01"/>

=== 事發經過 ===
[[File:Flickr_-_The_U.S._Army_-_Taking_cover_at_Fort_Hood.jpg|缩略图]]
[[File:Fort_Hood_shooting_map.png|缩略图]]

在當地時間約莫下午1時34分，哈桑進入其工作場所士兵預備處理中心（Soldier Readiness Processing Center）。在那兒，工作人員於部隊調度之前和部署返還之後，都會立即接受例行性醫療檢查。哈桑當時配帶其[[FN_Five-seveN手槍|FN Five-seveN手槍]]，並在其上安裝兩個各一紅一綠的[[雷射瞄準器|雷射瞄準器]]。<ref name="AP 5" /><ref name="ynn01">{{cite web |url=http://austin.ynn.com/content/fort_hood_shooting/hasan_hearings/274783/munley-testifies-in-day-6-of-witness-testimony |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-01-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718044350/http://austin.ynn.com/content/fort_hood_shooting/hasan_hearings/274783/munley-testifies-in-day-6-of-witness-testimony |archivedate=2011-07-18 }}</ref> 之後在他身上還發現一把舊型的[[史密斯威森|史密斯威森]][[.357麥格農|.357麥格農]]的左輪手槍，但他並未用其射擊任何人。<ref name="ABC 1" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2010/10/21/national/main6977971.shtml |work=CBS News |title=Prosecution to Rest in Ft. Hood Massacre Trial |date=October 21, 2010 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2013-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005013337/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2010/10/21/national/main6977971.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據目擊者所言，哈桑在一張空著的桌前坐下，並低下頭數秒鐘後突然站起，大聲叫喊著「[[大赞辞|真主至大]]！」，然後便開火。<ref name="Telegraph" /><ref name="KMBC" /><ref name="NYT 8" />目擊者說，哈桑最初是「以一扇狀的姿態向士兵掃射」，然後才瞄準個別士兵。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.statesman.com/news/texas/witnesses-in-fort-hood-shooting-hearing-say-hasan-974838.html|title=Witnesses in Fort Hood shooting hearing say Hasan returned to shoot same victims over and over|publisher=Statesman.com|date=August 24, 2011|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101018040137/http://www.statesman.com/news/texas/witnesses-in-fort-hood-shooting-hearing-say-hasan-974838.html|archive-date=2010-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>目擊者陸軍中士麥可·戴維斯（Michael Davis）說︰「其開槍的頻率幾乎是不停地在射擊。我剛開始聽到時，聽起來就像是一把[[M16突擊步槍|M16突擊步槍]]。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kwtx.com/news/misc/105303923.html |title=Hasan Hearing Blog Tuesday Oct. 19, 2010 |publisher=Kwtx.com |accessdate=July 23, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404074225/http://www.kwtx.com/news/misc/105303923.html |archivedate=2012-04-04 }}</ref>

[[File:Army_mil-55427-2009-11-07-171121.jpg|缩略图]]

{{Link-en|美國陸軍後備隊|United States Army Reserve|陸軍後備役}}上尉約翰·加菲尼（John Gaffaney）試圖襲擊哈桑以阻止他，但還未觸及哈桑即遭到致命槍傷。<ref name=ArmyTimes2 />文職{{Link-en|醫師助理|physician assistant}}麥可·卡希爾（Michael Cahill）也試圖以椅子襲擊哈桑，但隨即中彈身亡。<ref>{{cite web|author=All Things Considered|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=130543304|title=Testimony Begins In Fort Hood Shooting|publisher=NPR|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121225723/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=130543304|dead-url=no}}</ref>陸軍後備役專業軍士羅根·伯內特（Logan Burnett）試圖向哈桑丟摺疊桌以阻止他，但左臀中彈後便倒地，隨後爬到鄰近的一間小隔間。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/US/11/12/fort.hood.wounded.soldier/index.html |publisher=CNN |title=Wounded Fort Hood soldier: 'Blood just everywhere' |date=November 12, 2009 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930100151/http://www.cnn.com/2009/US/11/12/fort.hood.wounded.soldier/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據目擊者的證詞，哈桑跳過了幾個射殺文員的機會，反而是朝著穿著制服<ref name="latimes01">{{cite news | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/oct/21/nation/la-na-fort-hood-20101021 | work=Los Angeles Times | first=David | last=Zucchino | date=October 21, 2010 | title=Police officers describe Fort Hood gunfight | accessdate=2013-10-01 | archive-date=2011-02-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211223756/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/oct/21/nation/la-na-fort-hood-20101021 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、依照軍中政策而未攜帶個人槍枝的軍人開槍。<ref name="L.A.Times not among" />據說，有某一時刻，哈桑靠近正躲在一張書桌下的五名文員<ref name="dallasnews02">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dallasnews.com/news/nation-world/nation/20101019-Civilian-nurse-testifies-Maj-Nidal-6201.ece |title={title} |access-date=2013-10-01 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130121065112/http://www.dallasnews.com/news/nation-world/nation/20101019-Civilian-nurse-testifies-Maj-Nidal-6201.ece |archive-date=2013-01-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，他看著他們，用其手槍雷射瞄準器的瞄準點，掃過當中一位男子的臉，然後轉身離開並未開槍。<ref name="dallasnews02"/>

{{Link-en|美國陸軍部民事警察|Department of the Army Civilian Police|基地民警}}警官金伯利·莫萊（Kimberly Munley）當時駕駛著巡邏車趕赴現場，正遇著在士兵預備處理中心外的哈桑。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/21134540/vp/33879048#33879048 |title=NBCNews.com Video Player |publisher=MSNBC |accessdate=July 23, 2012 |archive-date=2009-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091115113122/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/21134540/vp/33879048#33879048 |dead-url=no }}</ref>哈桑向莫萊開槍，莫萊則用其9mm的[[貝瑞塔M9手槍|M9手槍]]與哈桑交火。哈桑的其中一發子彈擊中鄰近的天溝，其彈片則擊中莫萊的手，而後又有兩發子彈擊中莫萊︰第一發擊中大腿，第二發擊中膝蓋。<ref name="ynn01"/><ref name="latimes01"/>正當她因中第一發子彈要倒下時，第二發子彈便擊中其[[股骨|股骨]]而將其粉碎，同時也將莫萊擊倒在地。<ref name="ynn01"/><ref name="latimes01"/>哈桑這時走向莫萊，將她的手槍踢開使其勾不著。<ref name="CNN, num rounds"/>

當槍擊正在外頭持續著，護士及軍醫趕緊進入大樓，以皮帶關緊門戶，並趕去協助傷患。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/10/19/texas.fort.hood.shootings/index.html |publisher=CNN |title=Witnesses recount bloody scenes at Fort Hood hearing |date=October 20, 2010 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027031220/http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/10/19/texas.fort.hood.shootings/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 根據前往急救的護士所述，大樓內的地板上覆滿大量鮮血，他們甚至走路都無法維持平衡，難以走向傷患進行協助。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.woodtv.com/dpps/news/national/south/more-ft-hood-soldiers-to-testify-tues-_3615794|title=Help me, help me, I've been shot|publisher=Woodtv.com|date=October 19, 2010|accessdate=July 23, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514102934/http://www.woodtv.com/dpps/news/national/south/more-ft-hood-soldiers-to-testify-tues-_3615794|archivedate=2013-05-14}}</ref> 在大樓外，哈桑持續向逃竄的軍人射擊，這時警官馬克·陶德（Mark Todd）趕到現場，並大聲喝令哈桑投降。<ref name="latimes01"/> 陶德說︰「之後他轉身並朝我開了數槍。我沒聽見他說半句話，他就只是轉身然後開槍。」<ref name="Telegraph 3" /> 這兩人於是相互交火，而哈桑則中了陶德五槍後被擊倒<ref name="Stripes 1" /><ref name="MT 4" />，不省人事，陶德將其手槍踢開，並為其上了手銬。<ref name="AP 6" />

=== 事後結果 ===

一名調查員之後證實，在大樓內尋獲146枚用過的彈殼<ref name="CNN, num rounds">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/10/20/texas.fort.hood.shootings/index.html?hpt=T1|publisher=CNN|title=Fort Hood witness says he feared there were more gunmen|date=October 20, 2010|accessdate=2013-10-01|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118095120/http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/10/20/texas.fort.hood.shootings/index.html?hpt=T1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在樓外另蒐集到68枚彈殼，槍手及警方則共射了214發子彈。<ref name="CNN, num rounds"/><ref name="sig">{{cite web|url=http://www.beaumontenterprise.com/news/texas/article/Accused-Fort-Hood-shooter-ruled-sane-faces-978233.php|author=Sig Christenson|title=Accused Fort Hood shooter ruled sane; faces capital trial|work=San Antonio Express-News|publisher=Beaumont Enterprise|date=January 25, 2011|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124065319/https://www.beaumontenterprise.com/news/texas/article/Accused-Fort-Hood-shooter-ruled-sane-faces-978233.php|dead-url=no}}</ref> 一名治療哈桑的軍醫說哈桑的口袋裝滿了[[彈匣|彈匣]]。<ref name="WSJ 1" /> 當槍擊事件結束後，哈桑的口袋還有177發可用彈藥，裝在20發或30發的彈匣內。<ref name="CNN, num rounds"/> 這起事件，歷時約10分鐘<ref name="L.A.Times 1" />，導致13人死亡——12名軍人以及一名平民，其中11人當場死亡，另2人之後死於醫院，同時有30人受傷。<ref name="MSNBC 2" /><ref name="USA Today 3" />

最初，官員們認為，這起槍擊事件有三名軍人牽涉其內<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/world/view/20091106-234537/Seven-dead-in-Texas-military-base-shootingreports12dead, |title=31 hurt in Texas military base shootings – INQUIRER.net, Philippine News for Filipinos<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2013-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005010816/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/world/view/20091106-234537/Seven-dead-in-Texas-military-base-shootingreports12dead, |dead-url=no }}</ref>，另兩名軍人於是被拘留，但隨後獲釋。胡德堡的網站上貼出了一份告示，表示這起槍擊事件並非在演習。槍擊事件發生後，胡德堡基地以及週邊區域，立即被[[憲兵|憲兵]]以及[[美國陸軍刑事調查司令部|美國陸軍刑事調查司令部]]（CID）{{Link-en|封鎖關閉|Lockdown}}，一直到當地時間晚間約7時。<ref name="Statesman" /> 此外，[[德州騎警司|德州騎警]]、{{Link-en|德州公路巡邏隊|Texas Highway Patrol|德州公共安全部州警}}<ref name="Houston Chronicle" />、[[貝爾縣_(德克薩斯州)|貝爾郡]]警長辦公室代表，以及來自奧斯汀和韋科市的[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]探員都被派遣到該基地。<ref name="BBC" /> 美國總統[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]在聽取了對此事件的簡報後，就槍擊案發表了一份聲明。<ref name="CNN" />

2010年11月5日，事件發生後一年，52個人因其在事件中的英勇行為而獲頒獎章。<ref name="kdh01">{{cite web|url=http://www.kdhnews.com/news/story.aspx?s=46108|title=52 receive awards honoring actions taken at Fort Hood Nov. 5, 2009|publisher=Kdhnews.com|accessdate=July 23, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318073450/http://www.kdhnews.com/news/story.aspx?s=46108|archivedate=2012-03-18}}</ref> 有10名軍人獲頒{{Link-en|軍人勳章|Soldier's Medal}}，包括死於試圖襲擊槍手的上尉約翰·加菲尼。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forthoodausa.org/chapter_news.shtml |title=Chapter News |publisher=Forthoodausa.org |accessdate=July 23, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320014336/http://www.forthoodausa.org/chapter_news.shtml |archivedate=2012-03-20 }}</ref> 警官金伯利·莫萊和馬克·陶德因其在槍擊事件中阻止了槍手而獲頒{{Link-en|陸軍部長英勇勳章|Secretary of the Army Award for Valor}}。<ref name="kdh01"/> 2011年5月23日，文職{{Link-en|醫師助理|physician assistant}}麥可·卡希爾因死於試圖以椅子襲擊槍手而獲追授陸軍英勇勳章。<ref name="cahillmedal">{{cite web|author=ANGELA K. BROWNAssociated Press|url=http://www.theoaklandpress.com/articles/2011/05/24/news/nation_and_world/doc4ddb4ed8d84d7840012597.txt|title=Civilian slain in Fort Hood shooting gets medal|publisher=theoaklandpress.com|accessdate=July 23, 2012}}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 2012年5月，參議員[[喬·李伯曼|喬·李伯曼]]和眾議員[[彼得·金|彼得·金]]提議，立訂法律以使槍擊案的罹難者有資格獲頒[[紫心勛章|紫心勛章]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.yahoo.com/proposal-allows-purple-heart-fort-hood-victims-200728225.html|title=Proposal allows Purple Heart for Fort Hood victims|agency=Associated Press|date=May 9, 2012|accessdate=August 1, 2012|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103736/https://news.yahoo.com/proposal-allows-purple-heart-fort-hood-victims-200728225.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 眾議員[[約翰·卡特|約翰·卡特]]在[[第113届美国国会|第113屆國會]]中，提出立法以將此槍擊事件由標明為「職場暴力事件」改為「戰鬥相關」，這樣槍擊案的罹難者便有資格獲得相關的所有福利以及紫心勛章。<ref>{{cite news |title=Congressman Reintroduces Bill to Help Ft. Hood Shooting Victims |author=Ned Berkowitz |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/congressman-reintroduces-bill-ft-hood-shooting-victims/story?id=18502230#.UTKT8uM1bq4.gmail |newspaper=ABC News |date=February 14, 2013 |accessdate=March 5, 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125030042/https://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/congressman-reintroduces-bill-ft-hood-shooting-victims/story?id=18502230#.UTKT8uM1bq4.gmail |dead-url=no }}</ref>

